  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3601120/extras/833262487c299d1c2f030280594a1e53.poster.avif?t=1747232317\" width=740 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3601120/extras/833262487c299d1c2f030280594a1e53.webm?t=1747232317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3601120/extras/833262487c299d1c2f030280594a1e53.mp4?t=1747232317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A relaxing and cozy casual game where hundreds of adorable kitty levels await you! Match fluffy little ones and enjoy soothing gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3601120/extras/77b2adb45906afd2e17a5f64d126d554.poster.avif?t=1747232317\" width=740 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3601120/extras/77b2adb45906afd2e17a5f64d126d554.webm?t=1747232317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3601120/extras/77b2adb45906afd2e17a5f64d126d554.mp4?t=1747232317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >900+ levels with gradually increasing difficulty</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lots of different cats — mischievous, cute, funny, and serious</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cute graphics and sounds</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perfect for players of all ages — bring joy and positivity to yourself and your loved ones!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game was made by us, Andrew and Sergio.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thank you for your interest in <strong><i>Toffee Cats</i></strong>. We hope the game brings you a few pleasant moments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3601120/extras/932e1dcac39f98db0eff53d0e2ceb219.avif?t=1747232317\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3601120/extras_big/932e1dcac39f98db0eff53d0e2ceb219.avif?t=1747232317 width=800 height=400 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3601120/extras/833262487c299d1c2f030280594a1e53.poster.avif?t=1747232317\" width=740 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3601120/extras/833262487c299d1c2f030280594a1e53.webm?t=1747232317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3601120/extras/833262487c299d1c2f030280594a1e53.mp4?t=1747232317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A relaxing and cozy casual game where hundreds of adorable kitty levels await you! Match fluffy little ones and enjoy soothing gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3601120/extras/77b2adb45906afd2e17a5f64d126d554.poster.avif?t=1747232317\" width=740 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3601120/extras/77b2adb45906afd2e17a5f64d126d554.webm?t=1747232317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3601120/extras/77b2adb45906afd2e17a5f64d126d554.mp4?t=1747232317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >900+ levels with gradually increasing difficulty</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lots of different cats — mischievous, cute, funny, and serious</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cute graphics and sounds</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perfect for players of all ages — bring joy and positivity to yourself and your loved ones!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game was made by us, Andrew and Sergio.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thank you for your interest in <strong><i>Toffee Cats</i></strong>. We hope the game brings you a few pleasant moments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3601120/extras/932e1dcac39f98db0eff53d0e2ceb219.avif?t=1747232317\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3601120/extras_big/932e1dcac39f98db0eff53d0e2ceb219.avif?t=1747232317 width=800 height=400 /></span></p>",
